activities.name: running/jogging
activities.description: Good old fashion running. The simplest way to burn calories and get heart pumping. Can be done outside, in the gym or at home on a tredmill

variation.name: Tredmill Jog
variation.description: Too cold or too hot outside? Just go for a run on a tredmill at home or at your local gym!

activities.name: hiking
activities.description: Hiking is a long, vigorous walk, usually on trails or footpaths. If you love nature or are adventurous, this is a great choice for you!
activities.directions: Make sure you take the proper safety precautions and have proper equiptment! Enjoy a walk along a trail or nature path!

variation.name: Outside Hike
variation.description: Hiking on a path or trail outside!

activities.name: Walking
activities.description: Simply walking can be great excercise! Walking is a great way to warm up, or to burn calories over the course of a workout!

variation.name: Outside/nature walk
variation.description: life is too short not to enjoy the Great Outdoors! Go for a walk outside and enjoy nature, the city, or wherever you are!

activities.name: Skateboarding/ Longboarding
activities.description: Wiki:Skateboarding is an action sport that involves riding and performing tricks using a skateboard, as well as a recreational activity, an art form, an entertainment industry job, and a method of transportation
activities.directions: Make sure you take the proper safety precautions and always wear a helmet and pads!

variation.name: Street/Vert Skateboarding
variation.description: Wiki: Street skateboarding is a skateboarding discipline which focuses on flatground tricks, grinds, slides and aerials within urban environments and public spaces/n Wiki: Vert skateboarding, short for vertical skateboarding, is the act of riding a skateboard on a skate ramp or other incline and involves the skateboarder transitioning from the horizontal plane to the vertical plane in order to perform skateboarding tricks
